metadata.name: The Mermaid's Temptation
metadata.description:
In our world seas and oceans have been discovered and explored for centuries and it still goes on. A new era has come with the arrival of the metaverse.

Metaverse seas and oceans keep their secrets. Stars come together in a special way and all the secret things become clear in these paintings. 

Behold and feel them, those who lurk in the depths.

Painted in Golden Autumn, 2018.

P.S. Emotional outburst in darkest hours is the best way to see hidden things.
